'''Henning Janssen''' is a Dutch fantasy artist and freelance illustrator who made some [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] related work, such as the [[HenJ GrafX Calendar 2006]]. He was also a concept artist on the fan film ''[[Born of Hope]]''.
